just for myself so I don't forget any steps when adding new content

ADDING NEW TASK

1. Create new hu.df.darkwood.task.action.TaskAction object - don't forget to change the id
2. Create a new map in hu.df.darkwood.task.TaskData - create new Map variable, don't forget mapList.add.
    If it has resource requirements, create a new resourceMap also, and don't forget mapMap.put(id, resourceMap)
3. If it's an upgrade, create and initialize an object for it in hu.df.darkwood.main.GameState
4. If upgrade, create a new hu.df.darkwood.upgrade.Upgrade object for it
5. Create hu.df.darkwood.UI.DWButton object and add it to buttonList
6. Initialize task action object in hu.df.darkwood.main.DarkWood
7. Add the object to taskActionList
8. Add button to respective ActionPane (gather, build, etc)
9. Add actionListener to button

ADDING NEW STAT
1. Create new stat object
2. Initialize new stat object in hu.df.darkwood.main.GameState
3. add to statList
